<!---BENCHMARK-->

| Parser                                   | Diff |
| ---------------------------------------- | ---- |
| LMM megaparse                            | 36   |
| Megaparse with LLamaParse and GPTCleaner | 74   |
| Megaparse with LLamaParse                | 97   |
| Unstructured Augmented Parse             | 99   |
| LLama Parse                              | 102  |
| **Megaparse**                            | 105  |

<!---END_BENCHMARK-->

_Lower is better_

